  <brief_title>High-flow Conditioned Oxygen Therapy Versus Non-invasive Ventilation: Prevention of Post-extubation Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison Between High-flow Conditioned Oxygen Therapy and Non-invasive Ventilation in Prevention of Post-extubation Respiratory Failure. A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
